des: This skill will give you the next primaries/caucuses for the 2020 presidential election. Dates are subject to change, so make sure to contact your local or state elections office to register, learn more about your ballot, and check your local voting date well in advance of voting.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
